<li> generate and link to rubydoc</li>
<li> automatic support to eTag on client side</li>
<li> automatic support to eTag and lastModified on server side</li>
<li> doc: etag on client and server side</li>
<li> doc: render_resource</li>
<li> json working on client and server side</li>
<li> doc: transition DSL</li>
</ul>

